<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This article is about the legal code. For the West African dish, see <a href="/wiki/Yassa_(food)" title="Yassa (food)">Yassa (food)</a>. For the Biblical figure, see <a href="/wiki/Jesse_(biblical_figure)" title="Jesse (biblical figure)">Jesse (biblical figure)</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Yasa_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Yasa (disambiguation)">Yasa (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
