<li><cite id="CITEREFMorgan2005" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/David_O._Morgan" title="David O. Morgan">Morgan, David O.</a> (2005). "The "Great Yasa of Chinggis Khan" Revisited". <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://brill.com/display/book/edcoll/9789047406334/B9789047406334_s015.xml"><i>Mongols, Turks, and Others</i></a>. Brill. pp.&#160;291–308. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-90-474-0633-4" title="Special:BookSources/978-90-474-0633-4"><bdi>978-90-474-0633-4</bdi></a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2024-03-12</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=The+%E2%80%9CGreat+Yasa+of+Chinggis+Khan%E2%80%9D+Revisited&amp;rft.btitle=Mongols%2C+Turks%2C+and+Others&amp;rft.pages=291-308&amp;rft.pub=Brill&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.isbn=978-90-474-0633-4&amp;rft.aulast=Morgan&amp;rft.aufirst=David+O.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbrill.com%2Fdisplay%2Fbook%2Fedcoll%2F9789047406334%2FB9789047406334_s015.xml&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AYassa" class="Z3988"></span></li>
